Popular Nigerian street singer, Zlatan finally speaks out in an interview after been arrested by EFCC. Gistvic Reports. Zlatan said with all the claims made on him, he is not a Yahoo boy but an entertainer. He said:
“It was Naira Marley Birthday, I was too tired when we heard a knock and we opened and saw people on red jacket. It then occur to me that all what we did in our last video was about to become a reality.
Zlatan also said life comes with a lot of challenges when you are on your way to the top. WATCH VIDEO BELOW: https://r2—sn-ouxaob-5c8e.googlevideo.com/videoplayback Source